T1  - Bureaucracy and Professionalism: A Reconsideration of Weber's Thesis
AU  - Toren, Nina
Y1  - 1976/07/01
PY  - 1976
DA  - 1976/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1976.4400734
DO  - 10.5465/amr.1976.4400734
